{
  "chapter": 23,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十三回·摇船母女\n\n风四娘与沈璧君乔装成摇船母女，泛舟西湖，掩饰身份。秋色满湖，两人有感美景，心中却始终挂念萧十一郎。她们以月圆之夜水月楼之约为线索，静候神秘天孙的出现。夜航中，遇\"要命书生\"史秋山、霍无病、王猛三人登船，欲往水月楼赴宴。史秋山多疑好色，一再试探风四娘身份，双方言语交锋，暗中较劲。船至水月楼，灯火辉煌，宾客云集，史秋山终揭宴主之名——竟是失踪已久的萧十一郎。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "这两句话虽然已俗，可是用来形容西湖，却是再好也没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你以前来过？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你知不知道水月楼在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chuan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "船姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那里岂非就是水月楼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_chuan_gu",
      "text": "水月楼是条画舫？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chuan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "船姑",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "湖上最大的三条画舫，一条叫不系园，一条叫书画舫，还有一条就是水月楼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_chuan_gu",
      "text": "这条画舫有多大？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chuan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "船姑",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "大得很，船楼上至少可以同时摆三四桌酒席。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_chuan_gu",
      "text": "你们平常一天可以赚多少银子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chuan_gu",
      "speaker_name": "船姑",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我们哪里能天天看得到银子，平常最多也只不过能赚个几十文钱而已，只有到了春天……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_chuan_gu",
      "text": "你想不想到城里去玩几天？除了花钱外，还可以赚五两银子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你还认不认得出我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我实在想不到你居然还会一点易容术。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你难道没有听人说过，我一向是条夜猫子？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你想那个叫天孙的人，后天晚上究竟会不会来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "一定会来的，我只怕他来了，我们还是认不出他。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "只要他来，我们就一定会认得出。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你有把握？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "现在我们至少已有了三条线索。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "第一，我们已知道他是个很瘦小的人，而且总是带着条小狗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "听说你一脚踢死过祁连山的大盗半天云？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你就是用这双脚踢的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我只有这一双脚。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你这双脚看来实在不像踢死过人的样子。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我喜欢听别人说我的脚好看，你若是个男人，我一定让你摸摸。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "只可惜我不是……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "可惜我们这两天有事，否则我一定要闯上船去，喝他几杯。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你知道船上是什么人在请客？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你连主人是谁都不知道，也敢闯去喝酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "不管他是谁，都一样会欢迎我的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "因为我是个女人，男人在喝酒的时候，看见有好看的女人来，总是欢迎得很的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你好像很有经验？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "老实说，像这种事我实在已不知做过多少次。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "只可惜我不是男人，否则我一定要你嫁给我。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你若是男人，我一定嫁给你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "岸上人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "船家，摇船过来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "看来我们的运气倒不错，今天刚改行，就有了生意。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我们既然干了这一行，就不能把生意往外推。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "有理。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你真的会摇船？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我本就是十八般武艺件件精通，件件稀松。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你有没有不会的事？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "有一件。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我从来也不会难为情。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "客官们要到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "水月楼，你知不知道水月楼在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来他的豪兴到还真不浅。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "霍无病",
      "listener": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "text": "他是从初五开始请酒的，到今天已七天。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我佩服他。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "你佩服他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "text": "无论谁大醉七天后，还有精神高歌我都佩服。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "霍无病",
      "listener": "char_wang_meng",
      "text": "你怎么知道他已大醉了七天？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "text": "因为我知道他这人一向是有酒必醉的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "却不知有多少女人肯来陪他醉？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "霍无病",
      "listener": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "text": "这次他究竟请了多少人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "text": "江南一带的武林英雄，他好像已全都请遍了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "霍无病",
      "listener": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "text": "他为的是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我姓史，叫史秋山，太史公的史，秋色满湖山的秋山。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "text": "史大爷。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "不是史大爷，是史二爷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "text": "霍大爷。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我叫王猛，王八蛋的王，我是老三。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "姑娘你姓什么？叫什么名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 379,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "text": "我是个摇船的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "摇船的难道就没有名姓？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 383,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "text": "摇船的有没有名姓，大爷们都不必知道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "既然同船共渡，就是缘份，既然有缘份，又何妨问一问名姓？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "speaker_name": "霍无病",
      "listener": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "text": "妇道人家，总是不好意思跟男人通名道姓的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": "char_huo_wu_bing",
      "text": "我看她并不像害羞的样子。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 397,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_meng",
      "speaker_name": "王猛",
      "listener": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "text": "不管怎么样，人家既然不愿说，你又何必一定要逼着人家说？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 399,
      "line_end": 399
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我既然已问了，她又何必一定不肯说？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "text": "不敢？我为什么不敢？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 407,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "因为你怕被我问出你的来历。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 409,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "text": "一个摇船的女人，难道还会有什么见不得人的来历？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 413,
      "line_end": 413
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你真是个摇船的？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 417,
      "line_end": 417
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "text": "当然是。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 419,
      "line_end": 419
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我看你不像。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 421,
      "line_end": 421
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "text": "我哪点不像？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 423,
      "line_end": 423
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "从头到脚都不像。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 425,
      "line_end": 425
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "text": "我若不像摇船的，你说我像什么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 427,
      "line_end": 427
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "水月楼到了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 439,
      "line_end": 439
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你能不能跳过去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 453,
      "line_end": 453
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "text": "（摇头不语）",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 457,
      "line_end": 457
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你不想过去看看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 459,
      "line_end": 459
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "text": "（摇头不语）",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 461,
      "line_end": 461
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你不后悔？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 463,
      "line_end": 463
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "text": "我为什么要后悔？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 465,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "因为这次请客的，是个大家都想看的人。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 467,
      "line_end": 467
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "text": "是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 469,
      "line_end": 469
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_qiu_shan",
      "speaker_name": "史秋山",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "萧十一郎！",
      "tone": "得意",
